    "question_id" : 18571223,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>I know I'm a little late tothe party but thisworks pretty neat (our professor gave it to us)</p>\n\n<pre><code>public static byte[] asBytes (String s) {                   \n           String tmp;\n           byte[] b = new byte[s.length() / 2];\n           int i;\n           for (i = 0; i &lt; s.length() / 2; i++) {\n             tmp = s.substring(i * 2, i * 2 + 2);\n             b[i] = (byte)(Integer.parseInt(tmp, 16) &amp; 0xff);\n           }\n           return b;                                            //return bytes\n    }\n</code></pre>\n"
